# Whitepaper Technical Diagrams
#
# This directory contains SVG assets for the GuardianClaw Whitepaper documentation.
# All diagrams are self-contained with no external dependencies.
#
# Files:
# - 4-layer-architecture.svg    (800x320)  Architecture: L1-L4 validation pipeline
# - inputvalidator-detectors.svg (700x500)  Architecture: InputValidator detector hierarchy
# - memory-shield-v2.svg         (600x480)  Products: Memory Shield v2.0 flow
# - compliance-frameworks.svg    (700x400)  Compliance: CLAW protocol integration
# - platform-overview.svg        (900x400)  Platform: Agent Builder to Monitor pipeline
#
# Usage in MDX:
# ![Architecture](/images/whitepaper/4-layer-architecture.svg)
#
# Design specifications:
# - Dark theme background (#0a0a0a)
# - System font: Arial with sans-serif fallback
# - Color scheme: GuardianClaw green (#22c55e), blue (#3b82f6), amber (#f59e0b), teal (#14b8a6)
